    <title>Luton Borough Council's compulsory purchase order for Station House: decision letter</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Explaining the Secretary of State's decision about the Luton Borough Council (Station House, Midland Road) compulsory purchase order 2011.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This letter gives details about the Secretary of State’s decision on the Luton Borough Council (Station House, Midland Road) compulsory purchase order 2011. It explains that the Secretary of State has decided to confirm the order subject to a specified modification.&lt;/p&gt;

